Assignment 2.6. Week 4: JavaScript en het DOM.

Use the menu website from last assignment.
Add 3 filter options. When one filter is pressed
show only the dishes corresponding to the filter.
Make these filters with data properties.
Make sure you can disable the selected filter as well.

- Combination of filters needs to work.
- When all filters are disabled, show all products.
- Add animations which enhances the user experience.
- Each page is W3C validated.
- The JavaScript does not contain errors.
- The site is completely responsive up to 400px.
